  "description": "Swap the Layer's modifier between Multiply and Checkerboard and verify the pipeline stays live across each replace. Prepares its own canvas (clear + rebuild) so it runs from any device state: one Layout(Grid 32x32) + one Layer + one effect + one modifier, then replace_module cycles the modifier MOD slot Multiply -> Checkerboard -> Multiply, measuring after each so a broken swap (null buffer / wrong light count) shows up. Exercises the modifier-replace path the UI's drag-replace uses.",
